    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Parc des Bastions]]></title>
    <link href="http://playdegex.github.io/2010/11/parc-des-bastions/"/>
    <updated>2010-11-01T19:50:09+01:00</updated>
    <id>http://playdegex.github.io/2010/11/parc-des-bastions</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_o22J03lZ9Gw/TLHLVaVqrCI/AAAAAAAAza4/eAux5Ew6mH8/s1600/IMAG1301.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: right; float: right; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em;"><br /><table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tr-caption-container" style="float: right; margin-left: 1em; text-align: right;"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align: center;"><img border="0" height="176" src="http://1.bp.blogspot.com/_o22J03lZ9Gw/TLHLVaVqrCI/AAAAAAAAza4/eAux5Ew6mH8/s320/IMAG1301.jpg" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" width="320" /></td></tr><tr><td class="tr-caption" style="text-align: center;">Parc Des Bastions</td></tr></tbody></table></a></div>


<p><a href="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_o22J03lZ9Gw/TLHLboebhuI/AAAAAAAAza8/A5xydZFNXYc/s1600/IMAG1305.jpg" imageanchor="1" style="clear: right; float: right; margin-bottom: 1em; margin-left: 1em;"><br /><table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" class="tr-caption-container" style="float: right; margin-left: 1em; text-align: right;"><tbody><tr><td style="text-align: center;"><img border="0" height="218" src="http://3.bp.blogspot.com/_o22J03lZ9Gw/TLHLboebhuI/AAAAAAAAza8/A5xydZFNXYc/s320/IMAG1305.jpg" style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" width="320" /></td></tr><tr><td class="tr-caption" style="text-align: center;">Sandpit, Parc des Bastions</td></tr></tbody></table></a><br />When the sun is out the white wooden climbing frame in <a href="http://www.ville-geneve.ch/plan-ville/parcs-jardins-plages-bains-publics/promenade-bastions/item/lieu/parc-des-bastions/">Parc des Bastions</a> must be one of the busiest playgrounds in Geneva.<br /><br />There are some wooden hobby horses and one of the best sand pits in the area. The sand pit includes running water for excellent dam making opportunities.</p>
]]></content>
